publisher			TheShortAndTheTall							
publish_time	 2015年10月15日		
desc_long							评测						“If you like the kind of cooperative action puzzle game, and you are not afraid of difficult titles, keep it in serious consideration, because it is worth playing and a because it's not a genre rich of releases.”7.8/10 – http://multiplayer.it/giochi/the-body-changer-per-pc.html“The Body Changer: the videogame that makes us proud to be Italian”- – http://www.gamesprincess.it/2015/10/the-body-changer-il-videogioco-che-ci-rende-fieri-di-essere-italiani/“We feel to recommend the purchase the to all those who are looking for a challenging puzzle game and able to keep us glued to the keyboard for a long time.”7/10 – http://ilovevg.it/recensioni/the-body-changer													Nominations 2016									THE BODY CHANGER was nominated at the PREMIO DRAGO D'ORO 2016, a prize dedicated to Italian excellence in gaming, in 2 categories: BEST ITALIAN GAME and BEST ARTITIC ACHIVEMENT.																						关于这款游戏							一款 3D单机游戏，并拥有多人协作模式,故事发生在太空中一个封闭的蓄水站内。 玩家通过远程协控同步器and ，在不同场景下切换 同步器来完成任务. 拿起武器和敌人战个痛快吧！太空纯净水的未来就靠你了！. 3D第三人称射击游戏，原创 and ，并含有挑战的揭秘元素:一款 不可多得的 PC端游戏！故事模式 + 3 种竞技场模式，多种地图选择, 多种机型控制！发现并控制远在太空的同步器, 杀死太空中的敌人！通过激活控制器解决谜题，净化水源，拯救太空站！不同颜色的水对角色有不同的作用。获取不同的武器，对敌人惊醒多样伤害！炫酷的3D第三人称射击游戏，色彩鲜明，角色基萌！独特的游戏方式，通过激活器与不同道具互动 解决谜题在这只靠操作不动脑的游戏风靡的年代，本游戏会重新激活你的脑细胞！						
